BY TIMOTHY AGBOR, OSOGBO The Inspector-General of Police, Usman Alkali Baba, has ordered the posting and redeployment of some senior police officers to various departments, commands and formations in some parts of the country. A statement issued by CSP Olumuyiwa Adejobi, the Force Public Relations Officer, Force Headquarters, Abuja on Tuesday, said the posting was with immediate effect. Those affected are Deputy Inspectors-General of Police (DIGs), Assistant Inspectors-General of Police (AIGs) and Commissioners of Police (CPs). The postings and redeployments were said to be in line with the manpower development policy of IGP Baba which has to do with placing round pegs in round holes. <img decoding="async" src="https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0050.jpg" alt="" width="747" height="863" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-114289" srcset="https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0050.jpg 747w, https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0050-260x300.jpg 260w, https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0050-130x150.jpg 130w, https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0050-150x173.jpg 150w, https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0050-300x347.jpg 300w, https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0050-696x804.jpg 696w, https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0050-364x420.jpg 364w" sizes="(max-width: 747px) 100vw, 747px" /> <img decoding="async" src="https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0048.jpg" alt="" width="798" height="997" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-114288" srcset="https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0048.jpg 798w, https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA0048-240x300.jpg 240w, https://www.thepointng.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG-20230207-WA00